@TwitterClone.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5220

### Health check
GET {{TwitterClone.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### List tweets (newest first)
GET {{TwitterClone.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tweets
Accept: application/json

### Create a tweet
POST {{TwitterClone.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tweets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello from the walking skeleton!",
  "authorHandle": "@claude"
}

### Create a tweet that fails validation (empty content)
POST {{TwitterClone.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tweets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "",
  "authorHandle": "@claude"
}

###
